Text:
From the search results i found three BRRip releases from well known groups; This one, ResourceRG by Dusty's release, and ZEKTORM. If you prefer XviD there is also ViSiON's release. From what i was able to tell from the sample and portions of the films, this release has the best audio and video. But if you're looking for seeds they are as followed from highest to low:

Predators.2010.BRRIP.720P.H264-ZEKTORM
Predators.2010.720p.BRRip.XviD.AC3-ViSiON
Predators (2010).720P.BRRip.H264.ResourceRG by Dusty
Predators 2010 BRRip 720p x264 AAC - honchorella (Kingdom Release)
